keepConnect.name: Nna o golagantswe
keepConnect.helperText: Fa o tobetsa kgokagano ya Simolola, o bo o boloka kgokagano. Seno se tlhoka gore kgokagano e tla golaganngwa gape ka metlha morago ga gore e kgaolwe.
